&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Continuous Control Validation:&lt;/strong&gt

&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;The world of digital assets is accelerating in speed, magnitude, and complexity, opening the door to new ways for leveraging the blockchain. Fireblocks’ platform and network provide the simplest and most secure way for companies to work with digital assets and it trusted by some of the largest financial institutions, banks, globally-recognized brands, and Web3 companies in the world, including BNY Mellon, BNP Paribas, ANZ Bank, Revolut, and thousands more.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;Fireblocks is hiring a Senior Backend Engineer to join the Liquidity Team in Tel Aviv-Yafo, Israel.&lt;/p&gt;
