&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What you will be doing:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Lead Strategic Standalone Projects:&lt;/strong&gt; Take full end-to-end ownership of major product initiatives. You will move from initial market discovery and strategy to technical execution and global launch.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Define the &quot;Forter Experience&quot; Standards:&lt;/strong&gt; Create and document the innovative experience patterns and &quot;agentic&quot; flows that define how merchants interact with our platform. You’ll ensure these patterns are modular and high-quality so other PMs can easil

